-- в”Ђв”Ђ Creatio в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
UPDATE tools SET
  short_description = COALESCE($q$Creatio is a no-code CRM and business process management platform combining sales, marketing, and service automation with built-in AI agents.$q$, short_description),
  pricing_model = COALESCE($q$Subscription (per-user, minimum annual commitment)$q$, pricing_model),
  starting_price = COALESCE($q$$25/user/month$q$, starting_price),
  founded_year = COALESCE(2002, founded_year),
  company_size = COALESCE($q$700+ employees$q$, company_size),
  headquarters = COALESCE($q$Boston, Massachusetts, United States$q$, headquarters),
  languages = ARRAY[$q$English$q$]::text[],
  seo_title = COALESCE($q$Creatio Review 2026: No-Code CRM & BPM Pricing$q$, seo_title),
  seo_meta_description = COALESCE($q$Creatio combines no-code CRM, marketing, service, and business process automation with built-in AI agents; see its 2026 pricing plans and features here.$q$, seo_meta_description),
  llm_readable_summary = COALESCE($q$Creatio is a no-code CRM and business process management (BPM) platform originally founded in 2002 in Ukraine as Terrasoft, which later rebranded its product line as 'bpm'online' before adopting the unified Creatio name in October 2019. The company is now headquartered in Boston, Massachusetts, operates six offices with a presence in roughly 25 countries, employs more than 700 people, and has raised over $278 million in funding from investors including Volition Capital and Sapphire Ventures, reaching unicorn status (a $1.2 billion valuation) in 2024. Creatio's platform sits at the intersection of CRM and no-code process automation: it ships Sales, Marketing, and Service 'Creatio' modules built on top of a shared no-code development studio, so customers can both use out-of-the-box CRM functionality and visually build or customize their own business applications and workflows without writing code. The no-code studio includes a drag-and-drop process designer (BPMN-based), a visual data model builder, and Freedom UI page designers. Creatio.ai layers generative and predictive AI agents across the platform to draft content, score leads, summarize customer interactions, and recommend next-best actions inside sales, marketing, and service workflows. Pricing follows a per-user, per-month model with three core platform tiers: Growth at roughly $25/user/month for small and mid-sized teams starting with core no-code and CRM capabilities; Enterprise at roughly $55/user/month (some sources cite closer to $40-75/user/month depending on packaging) for larger organizations needing broader automation and integration; and Unlimited at roughly $85/user/month for organizations running complex, large-scale automation with no restrictions on use cases. On the Growth and Enterprise tiers, the Sales, Marketing, and Service Creatio modules are sold as separate add-ons at about $15/user/month each, while the Unlimited tier bundles all three modules at no extra per-user charge. Notably, Creatio enforces a minimum purchase commitment of roughly $10,000 per year, which makes it a poor fit for very small teams or solo users despite its per-user pricing structure, positioning it firmly as a mid-market-to-enterprise platform. Creatio is commonly evaluated against Salesforce, Microsoft Dynamics 365, Pipedrive, and other no-code platforms like Zoho Creator, with its key differentiator being the tight integration between CRM functionality and a full no-code application development environment rather than CRM alone. It targets industries such as financial services, insurance, manufacturing, and professional services that need both standard CRM workflows and the flexibility to model custom, industry-specific business processes without a dedicated engineering team.$q$, llm_readable_summary),
  status = 'published',
  noindex = false,
  sitemap_eligible = true,
  published_at = COALESCE(published_at, now()),
  updated_at = now()
WHERE id = '4f75ddaa-758b-4b98-b9a1-7abb4b581a78';

